   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DBP: Watertech Services and EnviClean</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To establish and run 2 One-Stop-Shops in slum areas in Kasese, thereby testing the business case for the One-Stop-Shop concept. The long term goal of the project is to establish at least one collection of 5-6 One-Stop-Shops and one assisting biogas plant, thereby providing sanitary facilities and waste collection to about 3000 individuals and producing op to 1900 kWh per day. The project will also educate the community on the importance of proper sanitation / sanitary behaviour positively impacting on the environment and on the health of the local population.</narrative>
  </description>
